ou em <strong>segundo lugar</strong> no prêmio <a href=\"https://agenciati.wixsite.com/premioinovacao2017\">Desafio SECOP</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"embed\"><iframe width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5HE4QNTnVoo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n		<style type=\'text/css\'>\n			#gallery-1 {\n				margin: auto;\n			}\n			#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n				float: left;\n				margin-top: 10px;\n				text-align: center;\n				width: 25%;\n			}\n			#gallery-1 img {\n				border: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n			}\n			#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n				margin-left: 0;\n			}\n			/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n		</style>\n		<div id=\'gallery-1\' class=\'gallery galleryid-391 gallery-columns-4 gallery-size-medium\'><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon landscape\'>\n				<a href=\'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/1.jpg\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-393\" /></a>\n			</dt>\n				<dd class=\'wp-caption-text gallery-caption\' id=\'gallery-1-393\'>\n				Prof. José Lopes <Líder Educacional Openredu.org>\n				</dd></dl><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon portrait\'>\n				<a href=\'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/2.jpg\'><img width=\"169\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/2.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n			</dt></dl><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon landscape\'>\n				<a href=\'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/3.jpg\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"169\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/3.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n			</dt></dl><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon portrait\'>\n				<a href=\'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/4.jpg\'><img width=\"169\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/4.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n			</dt></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon landscape\'>\n				<a href=\'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/7.jpg\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/7.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n			</dt></dl><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon landscape\'>\n				<a href=\'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/12.jpg\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"187\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/12.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-398\" /></a>\n			</dt>\n				<dd class=\'wp-caption-text gallery-caption\' id=\'gallery-1-398\'>\n				Recebimento da premiação de 2º lugar para o  Openredu.org\n				</dd></dl><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon landscape\'>\n				<a href=\'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/15.jpg\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"169\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/15.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-399\" /></a>\n			</dt>\n				<dd class=\'wp-caption-text gallery-caption\' id=\'gallery-1-399\'>\n				3 projetos vencedores do Desafio SECOP 2017\n				</dd></dl><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon landscape\'>\n				<a href=\'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/16.jpg\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"169\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/16.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n			</dt></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon landscape\'>\n				<a href=\'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/21.jpg\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"169\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/21.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-401\" /></a>\n			</dt>\n				<dd class=\'wp-caption-text gallery-caption\' id=\'gallery-1-401\'>\n				Folder Viitra &#8211; Empresa da incubadora Positiva UFPE\n				</dd></dl><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon landscape\'>\n				<a href=\'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/SELO-INOVACAO-ABEP.jpg\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/SELO-INOVACAO-ABEP.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n			</dt></dl>\n			<br style=\'clear: both\' />\n		</div>\n\n<p>O concurso ocorreu durante a programação do <a href=\"http://www.secop.org.br\">SECOP 2017</a>, realizado entre os dias 13 e 15 de setembro de 2017 no <a href=\"http://www.enotelportodegalinhas.com.br/default-pt.html\">Enotel</a>. A comunidade Openredu.org foi representada no evento pelo <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/jos%C3%A9-lopes-f-junior-9a09aa53/\">Professor José Lopes Ferreira Junior</a> &lt;jose.lopes@upe.br&gt;, Líder Educacional voluntário da Comunidade do software livre Openredu.</p>\n<p>O tema do evento foi <strong>TI Pública – Conectando o Governo com a Sociedade Digital</strong>, trazendo múltiplos olhares sobre a tecnologia para governo e, por isso, tem o papel fundamental de fazer a ponte entre setor público, iniciativa privada e a população.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','no'),(3053,'_transient_timeout_instantarticles_mod_422','1506713779','no'),(3054,'_transient_instantarticles_mod_422','-1-11-30 00:00:00','no'),(1864,'_site_transient_timeout_community-events-7618b82cfdd0292f569a788de3170195','1500471616','no'),(1865,'_site_transient_community-events-7618b82cfdd0292f569a788de3170195','a:2:{s:8:\"location\";a:1:{s:2:\"ip\";s:12:\"179.180.11.0\";}s:6:\"events\";a:0:{}}','no'),(1979,'hugeit_slider_title_has_margin','1','yes'),(1977,'hugeit_slider_title_text_align','right','yes'),(1978,'hugeit_slider_title_for_title_has_margin','Title has margin','yes'),(1974,'hugeit_slider_title_for_title_background_transparency','Slider ti