tece em São Paulo, no Anhembi e as inscrição são realizadas pelo site <a href=\"https://campuse.ro/events/campus-party-brasil-2018/\">https://campuse.ro/events/campus-party-brasil-2018/</a>. Para acompanhar a programação e saber mais sobre a Campus Party, basta acessar o site <a href=\"http://www.campus-party.org/\">http://www.campus-party.org/</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"addtoany_share_save_container addtoany_content addtoany_content_bottom\"><div class=\"addtoany_header\">Compartilhe</div><div class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_24 addtoany_list\" data-a2a-url=\"http://openredu.org/blog/o-futuro-da-educacao-openredu-no-campus-party-2018/\" data-a2a-title=\"O Futuro da Educação – Openredu no Campus Party 2018\"><a class=\"a2a_button_facebook\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fopenredu.org%2Fblog%2Fo-futuro-da-educacao-openredu-no-campus-party-2018%2F&amp;linkname=O%20Futuro%20da%20Educa%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20%E2%80%93%20Openredu%20no%20Campus%20Party%202018\" title=\"Facebook\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_twitter\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fopenredu.org%2Fblog%2Fo-futuro-da-educacao-openredu-no-campus-party-2018%2F&amp;linkname=O%20Futuro%20da%20Educa%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20%E2%80%93%20Openredu%20no%20Campus%20Party%202018\" title=\"Twitter\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_linkedin\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/linkedin?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fopenredu.org%2Fblog%2Fo-futuro-da-educacao-openredu-no-campus-party-2018%2F&amp;linkname=O%20Futuro%20da%20Educa%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20%E2%80%93%20Openredu%20no%20Campus%20Party%202018\" title=\"LinkedIn\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_google_plus\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fopenredu.org%2Fblog%2Fo-futuro-da-educacao-openredu-no-campus-party-2018%2F&amp;linkname=O%20Futuro%20da%20Educa%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20%E2%80%93%