>\n<li>Participar no fórum;</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Para concorrer ao prêmio é necessário realizar inscrição por meio do formulário disponível no link <a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/tJCKilmAcymNLQue2\">https://goo.gl/forms/tJCKilmAcymNLQue2</a>.</p>\n<p>Confira o Edital completo:</p>\n<div class=\'w3eden\'><!-- WPDM Link Template: Default Template -->\n\n\n<div class=\"wpdm-link-tpl link-btn [color]\" data-durl=\"http://openredu.org/download/edital-premio-openredu-paulo-freire/?wpdmdl=447\" >\n    <div class=\"media\">\n        <div class=\"pull-left\"><img class=\"wpdm_icon\" alt=\"Icon\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/plugins/download-manager/assets/file-type-icons/pdf.png\" onError=\'this.src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/plugins/download-manager/assets/file-type-icons/_blank.png\";\' /></div>\n        <div class=\"media-body\"><strong class=\"ptitle\">Edital Prêmio Openredu - Paulo Freire <span class=\"label label-default\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">217.08 KB</span></strong>\n            <div><strong>Download</strong></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>Errata <div class=\'w3eden\'><!-- WPDM Link Template: Default Template -->\n\n\n<div class=\"wpdm-link-tpl link-btn [color]\" data-durl=\"http://openredu.org/download/errata-premio-paulo-freire/?wpdmdl=454\" >\n    <div class=\"media\">\n        <div class=\"pull-left\"><img class=\"wpdm_icon\" alt=\"Icon\" src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/plugins/download-manager/assets/file-type-icons/pdf.png\" onError=\'this.src=\"http://openredu.org/wp-content/plugins/download-manager/assets/file-type-icons/_blank.png\";\' /></div>\n        <div class=\"media-body\"><strong class=\"ptitle\">Errata Prêmio Paulo Freire <span class=\"label label-default\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">185.43 KB</span></strong>\n            <div><strong>Download</strong></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</div></p>\n<p>Errata 2 <div class=\'w3ede