ma forma.<br /><br />Para a área de design você pode colaborar de diversas formas:<br /><ul><br /> 	<li>Criando material promocional;</li><br /> 	<li>Atualizando nosso guia de identidade visual;</li><br /> 	<li>Sugerindo melhorias de interface;</li><br /> 	<li>Melhorando o front-end;</li><br /> 	<li>Realizando testes de usabilidade;</li><br /> 	<li>Desenvolvendo melhorias para nosso Guideline;</li><br /> 	<li>Realizando palestras e eventos que promovam a plataforma;</li><br /> 	<li>Publicando trabalhos científicos a respeito da plataforma;</li><br /></ul><br />Caso queira entrar em contato com o a equipe principal de P&amp;D do <strong>Openredu</strong>, no Cin/UFPE, <a href=\"#\">CLIQUE AQUI</a>, teremos imenso prazer em conversar com você.[:en]The community is maintained by employees who, like you, are familiar with the project and would like to help in any way.<br /><br />For the design area you can collaborate in several ways:<br /><ul><br /> 	<li>Creating promotional material;</li><br /> 	<li>Updating our visual identity guide;</li><br /> 	<li>Suggesting interface improvements;</li><br /> 	<li>Improving the front end;</li><br /> 	<li>Performing usability tests;</li><br /> 	<li>Developing improvements to our Guideline;</li><br /> 	<li>Conducting lectures and events that promote the platform;</li><br /> 	<li>Publishing scientific papers on the platform;</li><br /></ul><br />If you would like to contact Openredu\'s main R &amp; D team at Cin / UFPE, <a href=\"#\">CLICK HERE</a>, we will be delighted to chat with you.[:]','Seja um Thinker','','publish','closed','open','','seja-um-thinker','','','2017-07-22 20:06:56','2017-07-22 23:06:56','',0,'http://openredu.tk/?p=163',0,'post','',0),(164,1,'2017-04-29 18:50:05','2017-04-29 21:50:05','','img-design-thinker','','inherit','closed','closed','','img-design-thinker','','','2017-04-29 18:50:05','2017-04-29 21:50:05','',163,'http://openredu.tk/wp-content/uploads/img-design-thinker.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(165