br\">http://openredu.ufpe.br</a> . Aqui no Site da Comunidade você encontra informações para<a href=\"https://github.com/OpenRedu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> baixar sua versão</a> e <a href=\"http://openredu.org/institutional/colabore/\">colaborar com o projeto</a> Open Source.[:en]Openredu is among the finalists of the SECOP 2017 Challenge and can bring the award of 10mil + ABEP seal to the Innovative project.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nThe SECOP DESAFIO Award is an incentive created by the Brazilian Association of State ICT Entities (ABEP) to promote and reward projects focused on innovative solutions for Government. This year, in its second edition, the opportunity will be open to candidates from all over Brazil. Each state technology entity will pre-screen.\r\n\r\nThe 4 finalists, in alphabetical order, are:\r\n\r\nCUBi (Egg I Kip);\r\nDevelopment of an Inference Engine for prioritization of Disbursement Requests in the State;\r\nHOME SCHOOL - HandsFree Institute;\r\nData Mining in the Identification of Irregular Companies regarding the Payment of Taxes;\r\nEducational Social Network - OPENREDU GPL2.\r\nTo learn more about the Challenge go to https://agenciati.wixsite.com/premioinovacao2017\r\n\r\nOpenredu is an Educational Social Network and is available for evaluation at http://openredu.ufpe.br. Here at the Community Site you will find information to download your version and collaborate with the Open Source project.[:]','[:pb]Openredu é um dos 5 finalistas do Desafio SECOP 2017[:en]Openredu is one of 5 finalists of the SECOP 2017 Challenge[:]','','publish','closed','open','','openredu-e-um-dos-5-finalistas-do-desafio-secop-2017','','','2017-08-24 14:36:33','2017-08-24 17:36:33','',0,'http://openredu.org/?p=377',0,'post','',0),(378,1,'2017-08-24 14:34:50','2017-08-24 17:34:50','','img-desafio-secop-2017','','inherit','closed','closed','','img-desafio-secop-2017','','','2017-08-24 14:34:50','2017-08-24 17:34:50','',377,'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/i