unity will be open to candidates from all over Brazil. Each state technology entity will pre-screen.\r\n\r\nThe 4 finalists, in alphabetical order, are:\r\n\r\nCUBi (Egg I Kip);\r\nDevelopment of an Inference Engine for prioritization of Disbursement Requests in the State;\r\nHOME SCHOOL - HandsFree Institute;\r\nData Mining in the Identification of Irregular Companies regarding the Payment of Taxes;\r\nEducational Social Network - OPENREDU GPL2.\r\nTo learn more about the Challenge go to https://agenciati.wixsite.com/premioinovacao2017\r\n\r\nOpenredu is an Educational Social Network and is available for evaluation at http://openredu.ufpe.br. Here at the Community Site you will find information to download your version and collaborate with the Open Source project.[:]','[:pb]Openredu é um dos 5 finalistas do Desafio SECOP 2017[:en]Openredu is one of 5 finalists of the SECOP 2017 Challenge[:]','','inherit','closed','closed','','377-revision-v1','','','2017-08-24 14:36:33','2017-08-24 17:36:33','',377,'http://openredu.org/sem-categoria/377-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(380,1,'2017-08-27 15:41:56','2017-08-27 18:41:56','[:pb]Os alunos da disciplina Análise e Gestão de Risco, no curso de Sistemas de Informação da <a href=\"http://www.faculdadesaomiguel.com.br/\">Faculdade São Miguel</a>, receberam os representantes da Comunidade Openredu e conheceram as possibilidades da ferramenta.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nNo dia 21 de Agosto de 2017, o professor Alex Sandro (Coordenador da Comunidade Openredu) e o professor José Lopes (Líder Educacional da GRE Metro Sul), foram apresentar o Openredu na Faculdade São Miguel, para alunos que cursam a disciplina de Análise e Gestão de Risco a Segurança da Informação, do 5º perído do curso de Segurança da Informação.\r\nSerá feita uma análise riscos na aplicação Openredu utilizando métodos da norma ISO 27005 e OWASP Top 10.\r\n\r\n[gallery ids=\"381,382,383\"][:en]Students of the discipline Analysis and Risk Management, in the course of Information Systems of Faculdade São Miguel, received the representatives of the Openredu Community and knew the possibilities of the tool.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nOn August 21, 2017, Professor Alex Sandro (Coordinator of the Openredu Community) and Professor José Lopes (Educational Leader of GRE Metro South), went to present Openredu at São Miguel College, for students studying the discipline of Analysis and Information Security Risk Management, of the 5th period of the Information Security course.\r\nA risk analysis will be done in the Openredu application using ISO 27005 and OWASP Top 10 methods.[:]','[:pb]Apresentação do Openredu para alunos na Faculdade São Miguel[:en]Presentation of Openredu for students at São Miguel College[:]','','publish','closed','open','','apresentacao-do-openredu-para-alunos-na-faculdade-sao-miguel','','','2017-08-27 15:53:24','2017-08-27 18:53:24','',0,'http://openredu.org/?p=380',0,'post','',0),(381,1,'2017-08-27 15:14:42','2017-08-27 18:14:42','','fsm-1','','inherit','closed','closed','','fsm-1','','','2017-08-27 15:14:42','2017-08-27 18:14:42','',380,'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/fsm-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(382,1,'2017-08-27 15:14:44','2017-08-27 18:14:44','','fsm-2','','inherit','closed','closed','','fsm-2','','','2017-08-27 15:14:44','2017-08-27 18:14:44','',380,'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/fsm-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(383,1,'2017-08-27 15:14:45','2017-08-27 18:14:45','','romildo','','inherit','closed','closed','','romildo','','','2017-08-27 15:14:45','2017-08-27 18:14:45','',380,'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/romildo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(384,1,'2017-08-27 15:14:46','2017-08-27 18:14:46','','romildo-2','','inherit','closed','closed','','romildo-2','','','2017-08-27 15:14:46','2017-08-27 18:14:46','',380,'http://openredu.org/wp-content/uploads/romildo-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(385,1,'2017-08-27 15:41:56','2017-08-27 18:41:56','[:pb]Os alunos da disciplina